# Terminal:

--> This is mainly for the mac machine
1. Install iTerm2.
2. Follow the instruction on this video to install the theme and color, https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D2PSsnqgBiw
This helps good visual appeal and readability for of the termnial

# Visual studio code:
Prefered code editor
--> Important plugins

1. Prettier - Code Formatter
2. Batch Rename
3. Code spell checker
4. ESLint
5. Jest, Jest Runner
6. JSON Beautify
7. Intellisense: NPM, Path
8. Peacock - Workspace color change
9. TODO: Highlight
